-- Primerica Names Ex-Citigroup CFO Crittenden to Insurer’s Board
-- B y   Z e k e   F a u x
-- 2013-07-15T21:28:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-15/primerica-names-ex-citigroup-cfo-crittenden-to-insurer-s-board.html
Primerica Inc. (PRI) , the life insurer
that used to be owned by Citigroup Inc., named  Gary Crittenden ,
the bank’s former chief financial officer, to its board of
directors.  Crittenden has been managing partner of HGGC since July
2009 and chief executive officer of the private equity firm
since April of last year, the Duluth, Georgia-based insurer said
today in a regulatory filing.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Zeke Faux in New York at 
 zfaux@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Kraut at   dkraut2@bloomberg.net  